# Root .ignore (Phase 0.6) — scope the vendor tree and generated files out of
# the agent's grep/read radius. The vendor tree is ~86k of the repo's ~88k
# Python lines and is READ-ONLY by standing rule, so nothing in it should ever
# enter a working session's search radius. The exceptions are the parts the
# refactor legitimately reads: vendor meta-docs, the patch queue, and the two
# verify scripts.

vendor/**
!vendor/
!vendor/*.md
!vendor/patches
!vendor/patches/**
!vendor/verify_core.py
!vendor/revendor_check.py

# Lockfiles — regenerated by uv/npm, never hand-read
**/uv.lock
projects/agent-web/frontend/package-lock.json

# Baselines and per-thread runtime state (large, machine-specific, not source)
baseline/
projects/agent-web/workspaces/
.pydantic-deep/
